---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About — Andrew Vieau"
			description="I'm a technical trainer & sales engineer based in Big Lake, Minnesota."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About</h1>

			<p>
				I'm an Enterprise Technology Generalist and full stack developer who has navigated the full lifecycle of the internet from writing flat HTML in Notepad to vibe-coding cloud-native enterprise level multisite solutions.
			</p>

			<p>
				I've spent the past decade bouncing between pre-sales and customer education.
			</p>

			<p>
				On the training side, I've hired and managed a team of trainers and learning experience designers. I led the transition from live bootcamps to digital-first delivery, piloting our remote program before COVID made it mandatory, and later implementing AI video tools to cut time-to-market on eLearning production.
			</p>

			<p>
				On presales, I've delivered tailored presentations across the full DXP stack (CMS, DAM, CDP, Personalization, and Commerce) from storytelling-focused demos for executive buyers to feature-centric technical deep dives for implementation teams.
			</p>

			<p>
				I also have a background as a French teacher, which has been incredibly important because for the majority of my career talking about tech has been very similar to speaking a foreign language.
			</p>

			<p>
				If there has been one unifying goal in all my positions, it's been helping folks understand complex concepts, and looking for that moment where everything clicks.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>